org.apache.drill.test

Class DrillTestWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.DrillTestWrapper

  • public class DrillTestWrapper
extends Object
    An object to encapsulate the options for a Drill unit test, as well as the execution methods to perform the tests and validation of results. To construct an instance easily, look at the TestBuilder class. From an implementation of the BaseTestQuery class, and instance of the builder is accessible through the testBuilder() method.
